1
 \left(\frac{1}{x^{a-b}}\right)^{\frac{1}{a-c}}\times\left(\frac{1}{x^{b-c}}\right)^{\frac{1}{b-a}}\times\left(\frac{1}{x^{c-a}}\right)^{\frac{1}{c-b}} =x^{-\left(\frac{a-b}{a-c}+\frac{b-c}{b-a}+\frac{c-a}{c-b}\right)} 
\frac1{x(a-b)(a-c)}+\frac1{x(b-c)(b-a)}+\frac1{x(c-a)(c-b)}
=-\frac1{x(a-b)(c-a)}-\frac1{x(b-c)(a-b)}-\frac1{x(c-a)(b-c)}
=-\frac{b-c+c-a+a-b}{x(a-b)(b-c)(c-a)}=0
